@remark s Images
@node "Images" "Notes about image-files"
@{b}@{u}Notes about image-files@{ub}@{uu}

Since version 2.0, it's possible to display nice images in  front  of  the
application  name.  I  have added a whole bunch of images to this archive,
but you can certainly create your own ones.


@{fg shine}Specifications@{fg text}

Format  :        Standard-IFF
Width   :        max. 64 pixel
Height  :        max. 64 pixel
Colours :        max. 8 (= 3 bitplanes)

If the format of the image exceeds one of these values  or  another  error
occurs, the image won't be loaded and only the default image is displayed.

@endnode
@remark e

